    public class DataDriverComboBox
extends javax.swing.JComboBox<DataDriver>
    This graphic user interface (GUI) component shows a combo box for users to select a data driver represented by DataDriver class.

      • selectDataDriver

        public void selectDataDriver(java.lang.String driverName)
        Select an item of data driver given driver name. Note each data driver always has a name. For example, the data driver for Derby engine database has name "derby".
        Parameters:
        driverName - specified driver name.
